    <name>m4s d</name>
    <summary>Universal Downloader &amp; AI Vocal Extractor</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
            m4s d is a production-grade C++17 / Qt6 desktop application combining two powerful pipelines in a single, non-blocking GUI.
        </p>
        <p>
            Download from over 1,000 websites using yt-dlp, and isolate vocals with zero music bleed using Meta's htdemucs_ft AI. It features full offline capability, bilingual Arabic/English UI, and seamless local file processing.
        </p>
    </description>

